Frequently Asked Questions

How old is Pau Gasol?

Pau Gasol is 45 years old.

Where was Pau Gasol born?

Pau Gasol was born in Barcelona, Spain.

When was Pau Gasol born?

Pau Gasol was born on July 6, 1980.

How tall is Pau Gasol?

Pau Gasol is 7-0 (213 cm) tall.

How much did Pau Gasol weigh when playing?

Pau Gasol weighed 250 lbs (113 kg) when playing.

Is Pau Gasol in the Hall of Fame?

Pau Gasol was inducted to the Hall of Fame as a Player in 2023 (Full List) .

When was Pau Gasol drafted?

Pau Gasol was drafted by Atlanta Hawks, 1st round (3rd pick, 3rd overall), 2001 NBA Draft.

What position did Pau Gasol play?

Center and Power Forward.

When did Pau Gasol retire?

Pau Gasol last played in 2019.

What is Pau Gasol's net worth?

Pau Gasol made at least $225,440,912 playing professional basketball.

How much did Pau Gasol make?

Pau Gasol made $19,285,850 in 2014.

What did Pau Gasol average?

Pau Gasol averaged 17.0 points, 9.2 rebounds, and 3.2 assists per game.

How many rings does Pau Gasol have?

Pau Gasol won 2 championships.

What is Pau Gasol's Instagram account?

Pau Gasol is on Instagram at paugasol.

What are Pau Gasol's nicknames?

Meal Ticket, ET, Kung Pow are nicknames for Pau Gasol.
